{"tid":1961724,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"綜合了泰國不同媒體的報道 總括今時今日泰國的情況","createTime":"2020-04-07T03:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T15:02:03.000Z","uid":73381,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"10bd36ca7f0096cbf6fff1af109a8d608a3dcc23","tid":1961724,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T03:45:05.000Z","msg":"泰國粉絲大本營 Thailandfans Forum<br />\n<br />\n綜合了泰國不同媒體的報道 總括今時今日泰國的情況：<br />\n<br />\n晚上10點至凌晨4點有國家宵禁<br />\n目前還沒有廿四小時的宵禁<br />\n所有航班一律禁止飛抵泰國直至4月18<br />\n允許遣返航班離開<br />\n大多數國內航班已暫停<br />\n沒有長途巴士<br />\n大約80％的火車被取消<br />\n各大省府的商場百貨公眾地方和娛樂設施都全面關閉<br />\n部份省府法例規定出外一定要戴口罩<br />\n部份省府酒店關閉<br />\n四月13至15所有潑水節活動宣布取消<br />\n<br />\n希望在這嚴格執行之下情況可以陸續轉好吧🙏🙏🙏"},{"pid":"3faa57fa071036de84764faea447c4818e9707a1","tid":1961724,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T03:53:21.000Z","msg":"巴打住泰國？<br />\n見你成日po泰國野<div style=\"text-align: left;\"></div>"},{"pid":"099d71a6c4869e5e9aca18ce75ca49a560d19a09","tid":1961724,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3faa57fa071036de84764faea447c4818e9707a1","tid":1961724,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T03:53:21.000Z","msg":"巴打住泰國？<br />\n見你成日po泰國野<div style=\"text-align: left;\"></div>"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:16:57.000Z","msg":"居泰港人"},{"pid":"65fd6c4cbcc6eb8628aa778a64123190b54ba150","tid":1961724,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"099d71a6c4869e5e9aca18ce75ca49a560d19a09","tid":1961724,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3faa57fa071036de84764faea447c4818e9707a1","tid":1961724,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T03:53:21.000Z","msg":"巴打住泰國？<br />\n見你成日po泰國野<div style=\"text-align: left;\"></div>"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:16:57.000Z","msg":"居泰港人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:51:29.000Z","msg":"退休？"},{"pid":"d3e300646e671bd951fea0e84df63ac48